titre: EBike Display SW102T LCD Screen Display 0-5 levels for BAFANG BBS01B BBS02B BBSHD Mid Motor Ebike Computer with PAS UART Protoco
titre_nb_auto: Elsykkeldisplay SW102T LCD-skjermvisning 0-5 nivåer for BAFANG BBS01B BBS02B BBSHD midtmotor elsykkelcomputer med PAS UART-protokoll
description:
Features

The EBike Display SW102T is a comprehensive LCD screen display designed specifically for BAFANG mid-drive electric bike motors, including the BBS01B, BBS02B, and BBSHD models. This user-friendly display provides essential information about your ride, allowing you to monitor and adjust your eBike's performance with ease.

  • Integrated 5-Level PAS (Pedal Assist Sensor) Control: Fine-tune your level of assistance with five distinct PAS settings, ranging from subtle support to powerful boost.
  • Bright LCD Screen: Enjoy clear visibility even in challenging lighting conditions with the bright and easily readable LCD display.
  • UART Protocol Compatibility: The SW102T seamlessly integrates with BAFANG motors via the UART protocol, ensuring reliable data transfer and communication.
  • Intuitive User Interface: Navigate through menus and settings effortlessly with the straightforward and intuitive user interface.

Specifications

The SW102T LCD display is crafted to meet the demanding requirements of eBike systems.

  • Display Type: LCD
  • Screen Size: Compact and easy-to-view
  • PAS Levels: 5 adjustable levels
  • Connectivity: UART Protocol for seamless communication with BAFANG motors
  • Mounting Options: Designed for secure mounting on your eBike handlebar.

Benefits

The EBike Display SW102T offers a multitude of benefits to enhance your eBike riding experience:

  • Personalized Ride Control: Tailor your eBike's power output to match your desired level of assistance, whether you prefer gentle support or powerful acceleration.
  • Enhanced Safety and Visibility: The bright LCD screen ensures easy readability in various lighting conditions, allowing for greater situational awareness during your rides.
  • Seamless Integration: The SW102T seamlessly integrates with BAFANG motors through the UART protocol, ensuring smooth data exchange and reliable performance.
  • User-Friendly Operation: The intuitive user interface makes navigating menus and settings a breeze, allowing for quick and effortless adjustments.

Usage

The SW102T is designed to be easily integrated into your BAFANG-powered eBike. Simply mount the display securely on your handlebars and connect it to your motor using the provided UART cable. Use the intuitive buttons on the display to cycle through menus, adjust PAS levels, and monitor essential riding information such as speed, battery level, and distance.

Regularly check your eBike's battery level and ensure proper charging to optimize performance. Consult the user manual for detailed instructions and safety guidelines specific to your BAFANG motor system.
description_nb_auto:
Funksjoner

EBike Display SW102T er en omfattende LCD-skjerm som er spesielt utviklet for BAFANG elsykkelmotorer med midtdrift, inkludert modellene BBS01B, BBS02B og BBSHD. Denne brukervennlige skjermen gir viktig informasjon om turen din, slik at du enkelt kan overvåke og justere elsykkelens ytelse.

  • Integrert 5-trinns PAS-kontroll (Pedal Assist Sensor): Finjuster assistansenivået med fem forskjellige PAS-innstillinger, alt fra subtil støtte til kraftig boost.
  • Lys LCD-skjerm: Nyt klar sikt selv under utfordrende lysforhold med den lyssterke og lettleste LCD-skjermen.
  • UART-protokollkompatibilitet: SW102T integreres sømløst med BAFANG-motorer via UART-protokollen, noe som sikrer pålitelig dataoverføring og kommunikasjon.
  • Intuitivt brukergrensesnitt: Naviger uanstrengt gjennom menyer og innstillinger med det enkle og intuitive brukergrensesnittet.

Spesifikasjoner

SW102T LCD-skjermen er laget for å møte de krevende kravene til elsykkelsystemer.

  • Skjermtype: LCD
  • Skjermstørrelse: Kompakt og lettlest
  • PAS-nivåer: 5 justerbare nivåer
  • Tilkobling: UART-protokoll for sømløs kommunikasjon med BAFANG-motorer
  • Monteringsalternativer: Designet for sikker montering på elsykkelstyret.

Fordeler

EBike-skjermen SW102T tilbyr en rekke fordeler for å forbedre elsykkelopplevelsen din:

  • Personlig tilpasset kjørekontroll: Tilpass elsykkelens effekt til ønsket assistansenivå, enten du foretrekker skånsom støtte eller kraftig akselerasjon.
  • Forbedret sikkerhet og synlighet: Den lyssterke LCD-skjermen sikrer enkel lesbarhet under ulike lysforhold, noe som gir større situasjonsforståelse under turer.
  • Sømløs integrering: SW102T integreres sømløst med BAFANG-motorer gjennom UART-protokollen, noe som sikrer jevn datautveksling og pålitelig ytelse.
  • Brukervennlig betjening: Det intuitive brukergrensesnittet gjør det enkelt å navigere i menyer og innstillinger, og gir raske og enkle justeringer.

Bruk

SW102T er designet for å enkelt integreres i din BAFANG-drevne elsykkel. Bare monter skjermen sikkert på styret og koble den til motoren med den medfølgende UART-kabelen. Bruk de intuitive knappene på skjermen til å bla gjennom menyer, justere PAS-nivåer og overvåke viktig sykkelinformasjon som hastighet, batterinivå og distanse.

Sjekk batterinivået på elsykkelen regelmessig og sørg for riktig lading for å optimalisere ytelsen. Se brukerhåndboken for detaljerte instruksjoner og sikkerhetsretningslinjer spesifikt for ditt BAFANG-motorsystem.

description:
Features

The Bafang BBS02B is a powerful mid-drive electric bike conversion kit designed to transform your bicycle into a capable e-bike. This robust system boasts a 750W peak power output, providing exhilarating acceleration and impressive hill-climbing ability. With its central motor placement, it offers optimal weight distribution and natural pedaling feel.

  • Mid-Drive Motor Placement:
    • Achieve balanced weight distribution and a natural cycling experience.
  • UART Communication Protocol:
    • Enables seamless integration with compatible displays and accessories for customized control and data monitoring.

Specifications

The Bafang BBS02B is engineered for performance and reliability. Here are some key specifications:

  • Motor Type:
    • Brushless DC (BLDC)
  • Power Output:
    • 750W Peak, 500W Continuous
  • Voltage:
    • 36V or 48V (depending on battery compatibility)
  • Torque:
    • High torque for excellent climbing performance.
  • Pedal Assist Levels:
    • Multiple levels to customize assistance intensity.

Benefits

This electric bike conversion kit offers a range of benefits for riders seeking enhanced cycling capabilities and convenience:

  • Effortless Riding:
    • Enjoy easier commutes, longer rides, and less fatigue with the power assistance provided by the motor.
  • Increased Performance:
    • Conquer hills with confidence and accelerate quickly for a more exhilarating riding experience.
  • Eco-Friendly Option:
    • Reduce your carbon footprint by opting for an electric bike over gasoline-powered vehicles.

Usage

The Bafang BBS02B is designed to be integrated into various bicycle frames. Installation typically involves mounting the motor onto the bottom bracket, connecting the wiring harness, and configuring the display unit.

Once installed, users can select their desired pedal assist level using the controller or display. The motor will then provide assistance proportional to your pedaling effort, making it ideal for a wide range of riding conditions and terrains.

Funksjoner

Bafang BBS02B er et kraftig konverteringssett for elektriske sykkeler med midtdrift, designet for å forvandle sykkelen din til en kapabel elsykkel. Dette robuste systemet har en toppeffekt på 750 W, noe som gir spennende akselerasjon og imponerende bakkekjøringsevne. Med sin sentrale plassering av motoren tilbyr den optimal vektfordeling og naturlig tråkkefølelse.

  • 750 W toppeffekt: Opplev uanstrengt akselerasjon og mestre bratte bakker med letthet.
  • Plassering av midtdriftsmotor:
    • Oppnå balansert vektfordeling og en naturlig sykkelopplevelse.
  • UART-kommunikasjonsprotokoll:
    • Muliggjør sømløs integrering med kompatible skjermer og tilbehør for tilpasset kontroll og dataovervåking.

Bafang BBS02B er konstruert for ytelse og pålitelighet. Her er noen viktige spesifikasjoner:

  • Effekt:
    • 750 W topp, 500 W kontinuerlig
  • Spenning:
    • 36 V eller 48 V (avhengig av batterikompatibilitet)
  • Dreiemoment:
    • Høyt dreiemoment for utmerket klatreevne.
  • Pedalassistansenivåer:

Fordeler

Dette konverteringssettet for elektriske sykkeler tilbyr en rekke fordeler for syklister som ønsker forbedrede sykkelegenskaper og bekvemmelighet:

  • Økt ytelse:
    • Besteig bakker med selvtillit og akselerer raskt for en mer spennende sykeopplevelse.
  • Miljøvennlig alternativ:
    • Reduser karbonavtrykket ditt ved å velge en elsykkel fremfor bensindrevne kjøretøy.

Bruk

Bafang BBS02B er designet for å integreres i ulike sykkelrammer. Installasjonen innebærer vanligvis å montere motoren på kranklageret, koble til ledningsnettet og konfigurere displayenheten.

Når den er installert, kan brukerne velge ønsket pedalassistansenivå ved hjelp av kontrolleren eller displayet. Motoren vil deretter gi assistanse proporsjonal med pedalanstrengelsen din, noe som gjør den ideell for et bredt spekter av sykleforhold og terreng.

titre: Ebike Hydraulic Brake Sensor Cable for Bafang BBS01 BBS02 BBSHD Motor Power Cut Off Brake Sensor Electric Bike Accessories

Features

This Ebike Hydraulic Brake Sensor Cable is specifically designed to work seamlessly with Bafang BBS01, BBS02, and BBSHD motors. It ensures a safe and efficient riding experience by cutting off power to the motor when either brake lever is activated.

  • Power cut-off function: Instantly stops motor power when a brake lever is squeezed, preventing unintended acceleration and promoting rider safety.
  • Direct connection: Easily connects to Bafang BBS01, BBS02, and BBSHD motors for plug-and-play installation.

Specifications

This brake sensor cable is constructed with durable materials to withstand the rigors of e-bike use. It features a robust design and reliable connections for long-lasting performance.

Benefits

By installing this Ebike Hydraulic Brake Sensor Cable, you gain several crucial advantages:

  • Enhanced safety: The power cut-off feature immediately halts motor power during braking, reducing the risk of accidents and promoting rider confidence.
  • Improved control: Precise brake integration allows for smoother stopping and increased overall control over your e-bike.
  • Peace of mind: Knowing that your e-bike is equipped with a reliable safety feature provides added reassurance during every ride.

Usage

To use this brake sensor cable, simply connect it to the designated port on your Bafang BBS01, BBS02, or BBSHD motor and the hydraulic braking system. Ensure proper wiring connections according to the manufacturer's instructions for optimal performance.

This cable is designed to integrate seamlessly with existing e-bike setups, allowing you to enjoy enhanced safety and control without complex modifications.

Denne hydrauliske bremsesensorkabelen for elsykkel er spesielt utviklet for å fungere sømløst med Bafang BBS01-, BBS02- og BBSHD-motorer. Den sikrer en trygg og effektiv kjøreopplevelse ved å kutte strømmen til motoren når en av bremsespakene aktiveres.

  • Kompatibilitet med hydrauliske bremser: Designet for å integreres med hydrauliske bremsesystemer for forbedret sikkerhet og kontroll.
  • Strømavbruddsfunksjon: Stopper motorstrømmen umiddelbart når en bremsespak klemmes inn, noe som forhindrer utilsiktet akselerasjon og fremmer syklistens sikkerhet.
  • Direkte tilkobling: Kobles enkelt til Bafang BBS01-, BBS02- og BBSHD-motorer for plug-and-play-installasjon.

Spesifikasjoner

Denne bremsesensorkabelen er konstruert med slitesterke materialer for å tåle påkjenningene ved bruk av elsykkel. Den har en robust design og pålitelige tilkoblinger for langvarig ytelse.

Fordeler

Ved å installere denne hydrauliske bremsesensorkabelen for elsykkel får du flere viktige fordeler:

Bruk

For å bruke denne bremsesensorkabelen, kobler du den ganske enkelt til den angitte porten på Bafang BBS01-, BBS02- eller BBSHD-motoren og det hydrauliske bremsesystemet. Sørg for riktig ledningstilkobling i henhold til produsentens instruksjoner for optimal ytelse.

  • Vanntett design: Mini SW102 har en robust vanntett konstruksjon, som sikrer at den tåler elementene og fungerer pålitelig under alle værforhold.

Spesifikasjoner

Mini SW102 LCD-skjermen er konstruert med presisjon og designet for optimal ytelse. Selv om de nøyaktige spesifikasjonene kan variere noe, er her noen viktige detaljer:

  • Strømkilde: Henter strøm direkte fra elsykkelens batteripakke, noe som sikrer en konstant og pålitelig forsyning.

Fordeler

Mini SW102 LCD-skjermen tilbyr en rekke fordeler for elsykkelsyklister:

  • Presis kontroll: Overvåk hastighet, batterinivå og andre målinger for å optimalisere elsykkelens ytelse og utvide rekkevidden.
  • Slitesterk ytelse: Den vanntette designen sikrer pålitelig drift under alle værforhold, noe som gir trygghet på hver tur.

Bruk

Mini SW102 LCD-skjermen er brukervennlig og enkel å betjene:

  • Installasjon: Monter skjermen sikkert på styret med det medfølgende monteringsutstyret.
  • Slå på/av: Slå skjermen av og på etter behov med den angitte av/på-knappen.
  • Menynavigasjon: Bruk de intuitive knappene til å navigere gjennom skjermens menyer og justere innstillinger.

titre: BAFANG Display DZ47 for M620 M600 M560 M510 M420 Mid Motors E-Bike Display Bike Computer with 0-9 PAS CAN Protocol

description:
Features

The BAFANG Display DZ47 is a versatile and user-friendly display designed specifically for BAFANG mid-drive motors, including the M620, M600, M560, M510, and M420 models. This sleek display offers a comprehensive range of features to enhance your e-bike riding experience.

  • LCD Display: The DZ47 features a clear and bright LCD screen that provides essential information at a glance, including speed, distance, battery level, assist mode, and more.
  • PAS Levels:
    • Provides customizable pedal assist levels (PAS) ranging from 0 to 9, allowing you to adjust the level of motor support based on your riding conditions and preferences.
  • CAN Protocol:
    • Utilizes the CAN protocol for seamless communication with compatible BAFANG motors, ensuring precise data transfer and accurate performance readings.

Specifications

The BAFANG Display DZ47 is engineered with precision to deliver reliable performance.

  • Display Type: LCD
  • PAS Levels: 0-9
  • Protocol: CAN
  • Compatibility: BAFANG M620, M600, M560, M510, and M420 Mid Motors

Benefits

The DZ47 offers numerous benefits that enhance your e-bike riding experience:

  • Enhanced Control: The customizable PAS levels allow you to precisely adjust the level of motor assistance for optimal control and efficiency.
  • Real-Time Information: The clear LCD display provides essential real-time data, empowering you to make informed riding decisions.
  • Seamless Integration: The CAN protocol ensures smooth and reliable communication between the display and your BAFANG motor.

Usage

The DZ47 is designed for easy installation and use.

To get started, simply connect the display to your compatible BAFANG mid-drive motor according to the manufacturer's instructions. Once connected, you can navigate through the menu options using the intuitive button controls to access various settings and display information.

description:

The Bafang UART Mid-Drive Motor Conversion Kit offers a powerful and efficient way to transform your bicycle into an electric bike. Designed for versatility, it's available in three power options: 750W, 500W, and 250W, allowing you to choose the perfect fit for your riding needs.

  • Durable and efficient mid-drive motor placement for optimal power delivery and natural pedaling feel.
  • Multiple power output options to suit various riding styles and terrain.

Specifications

This conversion kit includes a range of components designed to work together seamlessly:

  • Motor options: 750W, 500W, or 250W
  • Compatible with various crank arm sizes.
  • Includes necessary mounting hardware and wiring connections.

Benefits

Experience the freedom and convenience of electric biking with this comprehensive conversion kit:

  • Boost your pedaling power and conquer hills with ease.
  • Extend your range and enjoy longer rides.
  • Reduce strain on your legs, making cycling more accessible.

Usage

Installation requires basic mechanical skills and familiarity with bicycle components. The kit comes with detailed instructions and diagrams to guide you through the process. Once installed, simply connect the motor to a compatible battery pack and controller to begin enjoying your electric bike experience. Remember to follow all safety guidelines and regulations when riding an electric bicycle.

  • Flere effektalternativer som passer til ulike sykestiler og terreng.

Spesifikasjoner

Dette konverteringssettet inneholder en rekke komponenter som er designet for å fungere sømløst sammen:

  • Motoralternativer: 750 W, 500 W eller 250 W
  • Kompatibel med ulike krankarmstørrelser.
  • Inkluderer nødvendig monteringsutstyr og ledningstilkoblinger.

Fordeler

Opplev friheten og bekvemmeligheten ved elsykling med denne omfattende konverteringen sett:

  • Øk pedalkraften og erobre bakker med letthet.
  • Utvid rekkevidden og nyt lengre turer.
  • Reduser belastningen på beina, noe som gjør sykling mer tilgjengelig.

Bruk

Specifications

This e-bike conversion kit comes equipped with advanced components to deliver a seamless riding experience.

  • Motor Type: Brushless DC (BLDC) motor for quiet operation and high efficiency.
  • Torque Output: Offers significant torque, providing ample power assistance even on inclines.
  • Sensor System: Features a multi-sensor system to accurately detect pedaling cadence and deliver responsive power output.

Benefits

Transform your regular bicycle into an electric-powered companion, enjoying the freedom and convenience of e-assisted riding. The BAFANG BBSHD BBS01 BBS02B BBS02 BBS01B E-Bike Mid Drive Motor Kit offers numerous advantages:

  • Effortless Uphills: Conquer steep gradients with ease, thanks to the powerful torque output of the motor.
  • Extended Range: Pedal further and explore new horizons, leveraging the assistance provided by the electric motor.
  • Enhanced Efficiency: Reduce physical exertion and conserve your energy for more enjoyable rides.

Usage

This e-bike conversion kit is designed for use with bicycles that can accommodate a mid-drive motor. Installation may require some mechanical knowledge and tools. It's recommended to consult the provided user manual or seek professional assistance if needed.

The kit typically includes all necessary components for integration, such as the motor, controller, display unit, throttle (optional), and wiring harness.

  • USB Charging Port: Conveniently charge your mobile devices while on the go.

Specifications

The Bafang DPC020 CAN Display is built to meet the demands of modern eBikes.

  • Display Size: 3.4 inches

  • Additional Features: Integrated USB charging port

Benefits

The Bafang DPC020 CAN Display offers numerous benefits for eBike riders:

  • Enhanced Control and Visibility: Stay informed about your speed, battery level, distance traveled, and more with the clear LCD display.
  • Effortless Customization: Choose the riding mode that best suits your terrain and preferences.
  • Convenient Connectivity: Charge your mobile devices directly from the display using the built-in USB port.

Usage

The Bafang DPC020 CAN Display is designed to be user-friendly and easy to operate. Simply connect it to your compatible Bafang mid-drive motor using the 5 PIN male connector.

Navigate through the menus using the intuitive buttons on the display to adjust settings, select riding modes, and monitor your ride data. The USB charging port allows for convenient power access on the go.

titre: Bicycle Stem Adjustable 90 Degree Road Mountain MTB Bike Table 105mm Rod Front Fork Stem for 25.4mm Handlebar Power Parts
titre_nb_auto: Sykkelstem Justerbar 90 graders landevei Terrengsykkel MTB Sykkelbord 105 mm stang Forgaffelstem for 25,4 mm styre Power Parts
description:
Features

This adjustable bicycle stem is designed to provide a secure and versatile connection between your handlebars and fork, enhancing your riding experience.

  • 90 Degree Rotation: The stem allows for a 90-degree rotation, giving you the flexibility to adjust your handlebar position for optimal comfort and control.
  • Adjustable Length: Fine-tune the reach of your handlebars with the adjustable length feature, tailoring it to your individual preferences and riding style.
  • Durable Construction: Crafted from robust materials, this stem is built to withstand the rigors of cycling on various terrains.
  • Compatible with 25.4mm Handlebar: Designed specifically for handlebars with a diameter of 25.4mm, ensuring a secure and snug fit.

Specifications

The Adjustable 90 Degree Road Mountain MTB Bike Stem features a 105mm rod length and is compatible with standard front forks and handlebars.

Benefits

This versatile stem offers numerous benefits to enhance your cycling experience:

  • Improved Comfort: Adjust the handlebar position for greater comfort, reducing strain on your wrists and back.
  • Enhanced Control: Fine-tune your reach and control over the bike for a more responsive and confident ride.
  • Versatility for Different Riding Styles: The adjustable features cater to various riding styles, from road cycling to mountain biking.

Usage

To install the stem, simply follow these steps:

  1. Align the stem with the front fork steerer tube.
  2. Securely tighten the stem bolts according to manufacturer instructions.
  3. Attach your handlebars to the stem and ensure a secure fit.

Remember to always consult your bicycle's manual for specific installation guidelines and torque specifications.

description:
Features

The Bafang Mid Motor BBS01B/BBS02B offers a powerful and reliable electric bike conversion solution. Designed to seamlessly integrate with your bicycle, this motor kit delivers exhilarating performance and extended range.

  • Powerful Electric Drive: Available in various power outputs (36V 250W, 48V 500W, or 48V 750W), the Bafang BBS01B/BBS02B provides a substantial boost to your pedaling efforts.
  • Brushless Motor Technology: Experience smooth, quiet operation and increased efficiency thanks to the brushless motor design. This technology minimizes friction and maximizes power output.
  • Mid-Drive Placement: Strategically positioned within the bottom bracket (68mm BB shell), the mid-drive motor provides optimal weight distribution and enhances pedaling dynamics.
  • Versatile Installation: Designed for easy integration with a wide range of bicycles, this kit includes all necessary components for a successful conversion.

Specifications

The Bafang Mid Motor BBS01B/BBS02B boasts robust technical specifications to ensure reliable performance and durability:

  • Voltage Options: 36V or 48V
  • Power Outputs: 250W, 500W, or 750W
  • Bottom Bracket Shell Size: 68mm
  • Motor Type: Brushless

Benefits

By incorporating the Bafang Mid Motor BBS01B/BBS02B into your bicycle, you unlock a range of compelling benefits:

  • Effortless Riding: Conquer hills and long distances with ease, as the motor assists your pedaling efforts, reducing fatigue and enhancing your cycling experience.
  • Increased Range: Extend your riding range significantly by utilizing the electric assist, allowing you to explore further and enjoy longer adventures.
  • Improved Efficiency: The brushless motor technology delivers optimal energy efficiency, minimizing power consumption and extending battery life.

Usage

The Bafang Mid Motor BBS01B/BBS02B is designed for straightforward integration and operation:

Install the motor kit according to the provided instructions. Connect your chosen battery pack and control unit. Select your desired power level using the on-board display or controller. Pedal as usual, enjoying the seamless electric assist that boosts your pedaling force.

Bafang Mid Motor BBS01B/BBS02B tilbyr en kraftig og pålitelig løsning for konvertering av elektriske sykler. Dette motorsettet er designet for å integreres sømløst med sykkelen din, og gir spennende ytelse og utvidet rekkevidde.

  • Børsteløs motorteknologi: Opplev jevn, stillegående drift og økt effektivitet takket være den børsteløse motordesignen. Denne teknologien minimerer friksjon og maksimerer effektuttaket.

Spesifikasjoner

Bafang midtmotor BBS01B/BBS02B har robuste tekniske spesifikasjoner for å sikre pålitelig ytelse og holdbarhet:

Fordeler

Ved å innlemme Med Bafang Mid Motor BBS01B/BBS02B i sykkelen din får du tilgang til en rekke overbevisende fordeler:

  • Forbedret effektivitet:Den børsteløse motorteknologien gir optimal energieffektivitet, minimerer strømforbruket og forlenger batterilevetiden.

Bruk

Specifications

The Bafang DPC010 Display offers a range of specifications designed for optimal performance and user experience:

Installing and using the Bafang DPC010 Display is straightforward. Simply connect it to your compatible Bafang mid-drive motor, following the provided instructions. Specifications

The Bafang DPC18 Electric Bike Display boasts several key specifications that contribute to its performance and usability:

  • Intuitive LCD Screen: Features a clear and easy-to-read LCD screen for displaying speed, battery level, and other essential information.

  • Sleek and Compact Design: Its streamlined design seamlessly integrates with your e-bike's handlebars, enhancing its aesthetic appeal.

Benefits

The Bafang DPC18 Electric Bike Display offers numerous benefits that elevate your riding experience:

  • Enhanced Safety: The speedometer function provides valuable speed awareness, contributing to safer riding practices.
  • Increased Convenience: The integrated USB charging port eliminates the need for separate charging cables, streamlining your rides.
  • Improved Performance Monitoring: Access real-time information about your speed and battery level, allowing for optimized riding performance.

Usage

Installing and using the Bafang DPC18 Electric Bike Display is straightforward:

1. Connect the display to your compatible Bafang mid-drive motor according to the provided instructions.

titre_nb_auto: USB-programmeringskabel for elsykkel med 8fun/Bafang BBS01 BBS02 BBS03 BBSHD-programmeringskabel for midthjulsdrift/sentermotor på elsykkel
description:
Features

This specialized USB programming cable is designed to interface with a variety of popular ebike motors from manufacturers like 8fun and Bafang. It allows you to connect your motor to a computer for advanced customization and programming.

  • USB-C Connectivity: Seamlessly connects to both your ebike motor and your computer via the widely compatible USB-C standard.
  • Compatibility with Multiple Models: Designed specifically for 8fun / Bafang BBS01, BBS02, BBS03, and BBSHD mid drive electric bike motors.
  • Unlock Advanced Settings: Gain access to a range of customization options, including motor power output, pedal assist levels, speed limits, and more.

Specifications

Crafted with high-quality materials for durability and reliability, this cable ensures secure and consistent data transfer between your ebike and computer.

Benefits

Take control of your ebike's performance and tailor it to your specific riding needs. Adjust settings like power output to optimize for different terrains or riding styles. Fine-tune pedal assist levels for a more comfortable and efficient ride.

By connecting your ebike motor to your computer, you can delve deeper into its programming, unlocking customization possibilities that aren't available through standard controls.

Usage

Connect the USB-C end of the cable to your ebike motor and the other end to a compatible computer. Use specialized software (not included) to interface with your motor and make desired adjustments. Refer to the software's user manual for specific instructions on programming your ebike motor.
description_nb_auto:
Funksjoner

Denne spesialiserte USB-programmeringskabelen er designet for å kobles til en rekke populære elsykkelmotorer fra produsenter som 8fun og Bafang. Den lar deg koble motoren til en datamaskin for avansert tilpasning og programmering.

  • USB-C-tilkobling: Kobles sømløst til både elsykkelmotoren og datamaskinen din via den bredt kompatible USB-C-standarden.
  • Kompatibilitet med flere modeller: Designet spesielt for 8fun / Bafang BBS01, BBS02, BBS03 og BBSHD midtdrevne elsykkelmotorer.
  • Lås opp avanserte innstillinger: Få tilgang til en rekke tilpasningsalternativer, inkludert motoreffekt, pedalassistansenivåer, fartsgrenser og mer.

Spesifikasjoner

Laget med materialer av høy kvalitet for holdbarhet og pålitelighet, sikrer denne kabelen sikker og jevn dataoverføring mellom elsykkelen og datamaskinen.

Fordeler

Ta kontroll over elsykkelens ytelse og skreddersy den til dine spesifikke kjørebehov. Juster innstillinger som effekt for å optimalisere for ulike terreng eller kjørestiler. Finjuster pedalassistansenivåene for en mer komfortabel og effektiv tur.

Ved å koble elsykkelmotoren til datamaskinen kan du fordype deg i programmeringen og låse opp tilpasningsmuligheter som ikke er tilgjengelige via standardkontroller.

Bruk

Koble USB-C-enden av kabelen til elsykkelmotoren og den andre enden til en kompatibel datamaskin. Bruk spesialisert programvare (ikke inkludert) for å koble til motoren og gjøre ønskede justeringer. Se programvarens brukerhåndbok for spesifikke instruksjoner om programmering av elsykkelmotoren.

titre: Display Electric Bicycle Extension Cable Female To Male/Female To Female EBike Cable for Bafang Mid Motor Display Accessories
titre_nb_auto: Forlengelseskabel for elsykkel, hunn til hann/hunn til hunn, elsykkelkabel for Bafang midtmotor, tilbehør til display
description:
Features

This extension cable is specifically designed to work with Bafang mid-drive motor displays found on electric bicycles. It provides a convenient way to lengthen the connection between your display and the motor controller, allowing for more flexibility in bike setup and customization.

  • Female to Male Connector: One end of the cable features a female connector that plugs into your display unit, while the other end has a male connector that connects to the motor controller.
  • Female to Female Connector: Provides an additional option for extending connections by connecting two displays together or creating a longer run between components.

Specifications

This extension cable is constructed with durable materials to ensure reliable performance and longevity. The specific wire gauge and length can vary depending on the model, but are designed to effectively transmit power and data signals between your display and motor controller.

Benefits

By extending the connection between your display and motor controller, this cable offers several benefits:

  • Increased Flexibility: Position your display in a more comfortable or convenient location on your handlebars.
  • Improved Cable Management: Reduce clutter and tangling by lengthening the distance between components.

Usage

Simply connect one end of the cable to the female connector on your display unit and the other end to the male connector on your motor controller. For a female-to-female connection, plug two displays together using this cable.

Remember to consult your e-bike's user manual for specific instructions on connecting and configuring your display and motor controller.
description_nb_auto:
Funksjoner

Denne forlengelseskabelen er spesielt utviklet for å fungere med Bafang midtmotordisplayer som finnes på elsykler. Den gir en praktisk måte å forlenge forbindelsen mellom displayet og motorkontrolleren, noe som gir mer fleksibilitet i sykkeloppsett og tilpasning.

  • Hunn-til-hann-kontakt: Den ene enden av kabelen har en hunn-kontakt som kobles til displayenheten, mens den andre enden har en hann-kontakt som kobles til motorkontrolleren.
  • Hunn-til-hunn-kontakt: Gir et ekstra alternativ for å forlenge tilkoblinger ved å koble to skjermer sammen eller lage en lengre strekning mellom komponenter.

Spesifikasjoner

Denne forlengelseskabelen er konstruert med slitesterke materialer for å sikre pålitelig ytelse og lang levetid. Den spesifikke ledningstykkelsen og lengden kan variere avhengig av modell, men er designet for å effektivt overføre strøm- og datasignaler mellom skjermen og motorkontrolleren.

Fordeler

Ved å forlenge forbindelsen mellom skjermen og motorkontrolleren, tilbyr denne kabelen flere fordeler:

  • Økt fleksibilitet: Plasser skjermen på et mer komfortabelt eller praktisk sted på styret.
  • Forbedret kabelhåndtering: Reduser rot og floker ved å forlenge avstanden mellom komponentene.

Bruk

Bare koble den ene enden av kabelen til hunnkontakten på skjermenheten og den andre enden til hannkontakten på motorkontrolleren. For en hunn-til-hunn-tilkobling, koble to skjermer sammen med denne kabelen.

Husk å se i brukerhåndboken til elsykkelen din for spesifikke instruksjoner om tilkobling og konfigurering av skjermen og motorkontrolleren.

titre: Mid Motor Speed Sensor Magnet for BAFANG BBS01B BBS02B BBSHD Motor EBike Bafang Speed Magnet Middle Motor DIY Conversion Kits
titre_nb_auto: Midtmotorhastighetssensormagnet for BAFANG BBS01B BBS02B BBSHD-motor Elsykkel Bafang-hastighetsmagnet Midtmotor DIY-konverteringssett
description:
Features

This Mid Motor Speed Sensor Magnet is designed specifically to work with Bafang BBS01B, BBS02B, and BBSHD mid-drive electric bike motors. It's a crucial component for accurately measuring your bike's speed and ensuring proper operation of the motor controller and display.

  • Precise Speed Measurement: The magnet generates a magnetic field that interacts with the sensor, providing accurate readings of your bike's speed.
  • Compatible with Bafang Motors: Designed to fit seamlessly with Bafang BBS01B, BBS02B, and BBSHD motors.
  • DIY Conversion Kits: Ideal for use in DIY electric bike conversion kits, allowing you to easily add speed sensing functionality.

Specifications

This magnet is constructed from durable materials and designed to withstand the rigors of cycling. The shape and strength of the magnetic field are precisely engineered for optimal performance with Bafang motors.

Specific technical details such as dimensions and material composition may vary depending on the manufacturer and specific model.

Benefits

By ensuring accurate speed measurement, this magnet enables:

  • Optimal Motor Control: The motor controller receives precise speed information to adjust power output accordingly, providing smooth and efficient operation.
  • Accurate Display Readings: Your electric bike's display will accurately reflect your current speed, allowing you to monitor your progress effectively.
  • Enhanced Safety: Accurate speed data can contribute to safer riding by giving you a clear understanding of your velocity in various situations.

Usage

This magnet is typically installed on the motor itself. It interacts with the speed sensor, generating a magnetic field that allows for accurate speed measurement. Consult your electric bike's installation manual or specific instructions provided by the manufacturer for detailed guidance on installation and positioning.
description_nb_auto:
Funksjoner

Denne magneten for midtmotorhastighetssensor er spesielt utviklet for å fungere med Bafang BBS01B-, BBS02B- og BBSHD-mellommotorer for elektriske sykler. Det er en viktig komponent for å måle sykkelens hastighet nøyaktig og sikre at motorkontrolleren og displayet fungerer som de skal.

  • Presis hastighetsmåling: Magneten genererer et magnetfelt som samhandler med sensoren og gir nøyaktige avlesninger av sykkelens hastighet.
  • Kompatibel med Bafang-motorer: Designet for å passe sømløst med Bafang BBS01B-, BBS02B- og BBSHD-motorer.
  • DIY-konverteringssett: Ideell for bruk i DIY-konverteringssett for elektriske sykler, slik at du enkelt kan legge til hastighetsfølerfunksjonalitet.

Spesifikasjoner

Denne magneten er laget av slitesterke materialer og designet for å tåle påkjenningene ved sykling. Formen og styrken på magnetfeltet er presist konstruert for optimal ytelse med Bafang-motorer.

Spesifikke tekniske detaljer som dimensjoner og materialsammensetning kan variere avhengig av produsent og spesifikk modell.

Fordeler

Ved å sikre nøyaktig hastighetsmåling muliggjør denne magneten:

  • Optimal motorkontroll: Motorkontrolleren mottar presis hastighetsinformasjon for å justere effekten deretter, noe som gir jevn og effektiv drift.
  • Nøyaktige displayavlesninger: Displayet på elsykkelen din vil nøyaktig gjenspeile din nåværende hastighet, slik at du kan overvåke fremgangen din effektivt.
  • Forbedret sikkerhet: Nøyaktige hastighetsdata kan bidra til tryggere kjøring ved å gi deg en klar forståelse av hastigheten din i ulike situasjoner.

Bruk

Denne magneten er vanligvis installert på selve motoren. Den samhandler med hastighetssensoren og genererer et magnetfelt som muliggjør nøyaktig hastighetsmåling. Se monteringshåndboken for elsykkelen din eller de spesifikke instruksjonene fra produsenten for detaljert veiledning om montering og plassering.

Installing this BAFANG Chainring Chain Wheel Guard Sprocket Chainwheel on your BBSHD-powered ebike offers numerous advantages:

titre: Ebike Speed Sensor For Bafang BBS01 BBS02 BBSHD 250w-1000W CAN Version E-Bike Middle Drive Motor Speedometer Conversion Kit

description:
Features

This eBike speed sensor is specifically designed for Bafang BBS01, BBS02, and BBSHD mid-drive motors with a CAN bus communication system. It's a direct conversion kit to upgrade your existing setup and integrate a speedometer.

  • Speedometer Integration: Enables accurate speed readings on your display, providing valuable feedback during your rides.
  • Simple Installation: Designed for a straightforward installation process, minimizing downtime and complexity.

Specifications

The sensor is built to withstand the demands of eBike usage. Its compact design ensures a clean and integrated look on your bike. The sensor transmits speed data via the CAN bus protocol, ensuring compatibility with modern eBike systems.

Sensor Type: Hall Effect

Benefits

By installing this speed sensor, you can enjoy a range of benefits:

  • Enhanced Riding Experience: Accurately monitor your speed for better awareness and control.
  • Data-Driven Insights: Analyze your riding patterns and improve efficiency over time.
  • Improved Safety: Stay informed about your speed, especially in traffic or changing conditions.

Usage

This speed sensor is intended for use with Bafang BBS01, BBS02, and BBSHD mid-drive motors equipped with a CAN bus communication system. Consult your motor's user manual for specific installation instructions and wiring diagrams.

titre: BAFANG Crank Arms Cranksets for Bafang BBS01 BBS02 BBS03 BBSHD Mid Drive Motor Electric Bike Conversion Kit Parts & Accessories

description:
Features

These BAFANG crank arms are specifically designed to work seamlessly with BAFANG mid-drive motor systems like the BBS01, BBS02, BBS03, and BBSHD. Crafted for performance and durability, they provide a reliable connection between your pedals and the powerful Bafang motor, ensuring smooth and efficient power transfer.

  • Compatible with BAFANG mid-drive motors: BBS01, BBS02, BBS03, and BBSHD
  • Durable construction for long-lasting performance
  • Precision engineering for smooth power transfer
  • Ideal for electric bike conversion kits

Specifications

The BAFANG crank arms are manufactured to meet the demands of electric bicycle systems. They feature a robust design and specific gearing ratios optimized for efficient power delivery.

  • Material: High-strength aluminum alloy
  • Chainring Compatibility: Suitable for standard single-speed or multi-speed chainrings
  • Spindle Length: Designed to fit most BB shells (please refer to your motor's specifications for confirmation)

Benefits

By upgrading your electric bike with these BAFANG crank arms, you gain several advantages:

  • Enhanced Power Transfer: Experience a more direct and efficient connection between your pedaling effort and the motor's output.
  • Improved Durability: The robust construction withstands the stresses of frequent use and demanding terrain.
  • Seamless Integration: Designed specifically for BAFANG motors, ensuring a perfect fit and optimal performance.

Usage

These crank arms are designed to be used in conjunction with a Bafang mid-drive motor conversion kit. They replace the existing crank arms on your bicycle frame, connecting your pedals to the motor through the bottom bracket shell. Follow the installation instructions provided with your conversion kit for proper assembly and alignment.

Remember to consult your bike's owner's manual and the Bafang motor's specifications for detailed information about compatibility and installation procedures.

  • Non-Slip Grip: A textured palm surface ensures a secure grip on your handlebars, reducing the chance of slippage during rides.
  • Wrist Support: The gloves feature wrist support to help stabilize your wrists and reduce strain during long rides or aggressive maneuvers.

Specifications

These cycling gloves come in a variety of sizes to ensure a comfortable fit for most riders. They are designed to be lightweight and flexible, allowing for a full range of motion.

Benefits

By wearing these gloves, you can experience several benefits:

  • Reduced Hand Fatigue: The gel padding and breathable fabric help minimize hand fatigue during long rides.
  • Improved Grip and Control: The non-slip grip enhances your control over the handlebars, giving you greater confidence on the road or trail.
  • Enhanced Wrist Support: The wrist support helps prevent injuries and discomfort while riding.
  • Increased Comfort: The combination of breathable fabric, gel padding, and a comfortable fit makes these gloves ideal for extended use.

Usage

These cycling gloves are perfect for a variety of riding conditions. They are suitable for road cycling, mountain biking, BMX, and other cycling disciplines.

titre: Bafang C965 LCD Display Speed Indicator Electric Bicycle Conversion Mid Motor Hub Motor BBS01B BBS02B 36V 48V 750W E-bike Kits
titre_nb_auto: Bafang C965 LCD-skjerm Hastighetsindikator Elsykkelkonvertering Midtmotor Navmotor BBS01B BBS02B 36V 48V 750W Elsykkelsett
description:
Features

The Bafang C965 LCD Display is a powerful and versatile accessory designed to enhance your electric bicycle riding experience. This display seamlessly integrates with Bafang's popular BBS01B and BBS02B mid-drive motors, providing riders with essential information and control over their e-bike.

  • Speed Indicator: Clearly displays your current speed, allowing you to maintain a safe and efficient pace.
  • Battery Level Indicator: Monitors the remaining battery power, ensuring you know when it's time to recharge.
  • Cruise Control: Enable hands-free riding at a set speed for increased comfort on flat terrain.
  • Walk Assist Function: Provides assistance while walking your e-bike, making it easier to navigate crowded areas or hills.

Specifications

The Bafang C965 LCD Display is compatible with a range of voltage and wattage configurations:

  • Voltage: 36V or 48V
  • Wattage: 750W

Benefits

The Bafang C965 LCD Display offers numerous benefits to e-bike riders:

  • Enhanced Safety: The speed indicator and battery level monitoring features contribute to a safer riding experience.
  • Improved Comfort: Cruise control and walk assist functions reduce rider fatigue and effort.
  • Greater Control: Real-time data display allows for precise adjustment of riding parameters.

Usage

Installing the Bafang C965 LCD Display is relatively straightforward, typically involving connecting it to your Bafang BBS01B or BBS02B motor and wiring it to your bike's battery system. The display will then power on automatically when the system is activated. Refer to the manufacturer's instructions for detailed installation and operation guidelines.

With its intuitive interface and informative display, the Bafang C965 LCD Display empowers you to enjoy a safer, more efficient, and ultimately more enjoyable electric bicycle riding experience.

  • Gåassistentfunksjon: Gir hjelp mens du går på elsykkelen din, noe som gjør det enklere å navigere i overfylte områder eller bakker.

Spesifikasjoner

Bafang C965 LCD-skjermen er kompatibel med en rekke spennings- og wattstyrkekonfigurasjoner:

  • Wattstyrke: 750W

Fordeler

Bafang C965 LCD-skjermen tilbyr en rekke fordeler for elsykkelsyklister:

Bruk

Varstrom TSDZ8 elsykkelsett gir deg muligheten til å utforske nye horisonter med uanstrengt kraft og forbedret glede. Oppgrader sykkelen din i dag og lås opp en verden av muligheter.

titre: Bafang 48V 52V 1000W Mid Drive Motor BBSHD BBS03 eBike Kits BB 68/100/120mm Powerful Bicycle Engine Electric Bike Conversion Kit
titre_nb_auto: Bafang 48V 52V 1000W midtmotor BBSHD BBS03 elsykkelsett BB 68/100/120mm kraftig sykkelmotor konverteringssett for elsykkel
description:
Features

This Bafang mid-drive motor kit is designed for serious e-bikers looking to boost their riding experience. With a powerful motor and robust construction, it's perfect for tackling hills, hauling cargo, and enjoying longer rides.

  • Mid-Drive Motor: Positioned in the center of your bike frame, this motor provides natural pedaling feel and superior torque compared to hub motors.
  • Multiple Voltage Options: Available in both 48V and 52V configurations, you can choose the voltage best suited for your needs and battery capacity.
  • 1000W Power Output: Conquer any terrain with ease. This motor delivers ample power for hauling heavy loads and tackling steep inclines.
  • BBSHD & BBS03 Options: Select from the proven BBSHD model known for its reliability, or choose the versatile BBS03 for a wider range of compatibility.

Specifications

This eBike conversion kit is built with high-quality components and features several customizable options to ensure a perfect fit for your bike.

  • Motor Type: Mid-Drive
  • Voltage Options: 48V, 52V
  • Power Output: 1000W
  • Cassette Compatibility: Various options available for different gear ratios.
  • Bottom Bracket Shell Widths: Available in 68mm, 100mm, and 120mm to fit most common frames.

Benefits

By choosing this Bafang eBike conversion kit, you'll experience a host of benefits that will transform your riding:

  • Increased Range & Power: The powerful motor provides a significant boost to your pedaling effort, allowing you to cover longer distances and tackle challenging terrain with ease.
  • Enhanced Comfort & Performance: Enjoy effortless rides by letting the motor assist you on hills and flat surfaces. Reduce fatigue and arrive at your destination feeling refreshed.
  • Versatile Customization: With various voltage options, power levels, and bottom bracket shell widths, this kit can be tailored to your specific bike and riding style.

Usage

Installing this eBike conversion kit is relatively straightforward. The kit comes with detailed instructions and all the necessary components for a successful conversion. It's recommended to have basic mechanical skills or consult with an experienced bicycle mechanic for assistance during the installation process.

Once installed, you can easily activate the motor assist using the provided handlebar control unit. Adjust the assist level to your preference and enjoy the enhanced power and range of your eBike.
description_nb_auto:
Funksjoner

Dette Bafang midtmotorsettet er designet for seriøse elsyklister som ønsker å forbedre kjøreopplevelsen. Med en kraftig motor og robust konstruksjon er den perfekt for å takle bakker, frakte last og nyte lengre turer.

  • Midtmotor: Denne motoren er plassert i midten av sykkelrammen, og gir en naturlig tråkkefølelse og overlegent dreiemoment sammenlignet med navmotorer.
  • Flere spenningsalternativer: Tilgjengelig i både 48V og 52V konfigurasjoner, slik at du kan velge spenningen som passer best for dine behov og batterikapasitet.
  • 1000W effekt: Erobre ethvert terreng med letthet. Denne motoren leverer rikelig med kraft for å frakte tunge lass og takle bratte bakker.
  • BBSHD- og BBS03-alternativer: Velg fra den velprøvde BBSHD-modellen som er kjent for sin pålitelighet, eller velg den allsidige BBS03 for et bredere spekter av kompatibilitet.

Spesifikasjoner

Dette elsykkelkonverteringssettet er bygget med komponenter av høy kvalitet og har flere tilpassbare alternativer for å sikre en perfekt passform for sykkelen din.

  • Motortype: Midtdrev
  • Spenningsalternativer: 48V, 52V
  • Effekt: 1000W
  • Kassettkompatibilitet: Ulike alternativer tilgjengelig for forskjellige girforhold.
  • Kranklagerskallbredder: Tilgjengelig i 68 mm, 100 mm og 120 mm for å passe til de fleste vanlige rammer.

Fordeler

Ved å velge dette Bafang elsykkelkonverteringssettet, Du vil oppleve en rekke fordeler som vil forvandle syklingen din:

  • Økt rekkevidde og kraft: Den kraftige motoren gir en betydelig økning i tråkkkraften din, slik at du kan tilbakelegge lengre avstander og takle utfordrende terreng med letthet.
  • Forbedret komfort og ytelse: Nyt uanstrengte turer ved å la motoren hjelpe deg i bakker og flate overflater. Reduser tretthet og kom frem til reisemålet ditt med en uthvilt følelse.
  • Allsidig tilpasning: Med forskjellige spenningsalternativer, effektnivåer og kranklagerskallebredder kan dette settet skreddersys til din spesifikke sykkel og kjørestil.

Bruk

Det er relativt enkelt å installere dette elsykkelkonverteringssettet. Settet leveres med detaljerte instruksjoner og alle nødvendige komponenter for en vellykket konvertering. Det anbefales å ha grunnleggende mekaniske ferdigheter eller konsultere en erfaren sykkelmekaniker for å få hjelp under installasjonsprosessen.

Når det er installert, kan du enkelt aktivere motorassistansen ved hjelp av den medfølgende styrekontrollenheten. Juster assistansenivået etter dine preferanser og nyt den forbedrede kraften og rekkevidden til elsykkelen din.

titre: Bafang 48V 750W BBS02B Electric Bicycle Conversion Kits 8fun M315 Mid Drive Motor Bike Fit for BB Size 68mm-73mm/100mm Engine
titre_nb_auto: Bafang 48V 750W BBS02B elsykkelkonverteringssett 8fun M315 midthjulsmotorsykkel passer til BB-størrelse 68mm-73mm/100mm motor
description:
Features

The Bafang 48V 750W BBS02B Electric Bicycle Conversion Kit is a powerful and versatile system designed to transform your bicycle into an electric bike. It features an 8fun M315 mid-drive motor, known for its efficiency and smooth power delivery.

  • Mid-Drive Motor: The heart of the kit is the 8fun M315 mid-drive motor, which provides torque to the rear wheel through your bike's existing drivetrain. This placement offers superior weight distribution and efficient power transfer.
  • High Power Output: With a powerful 750W rating, this kit delivers ample assistance for tackling hills and navigating challenging terrain.
  • 48V System Voltage: The 48V system voltage ensures optimal performance and long-lasting battery life.
  • BB Size Compatibility: Designed to fit a wide range of bicycles, this kit is compatible with bottom bracket (BB) sizes ranging from 68mm to 73mm.

Specifications

The Bafang 45V 750W BBS02B Electric Bicycle Conversion Kit boasts several key specifications that contribute to its performance and reliability:

  • Motor Type: 8fun M315 Mid-Drive Motor
  • Power Output: 750W
  • Voltage: 48V
  • Bottom Bracket Size Compatibility: 68mm - 73mm, 100mm

Benefits

Converting your bicycle to an electric bike with the Bafang 48V 750W BBS02B kit offers numerous benefits:

  • Effortless Riding: The powerful motor assists you, making hills and long distances less strenuous.
  • Enhanced Range: Extend your cycling range significantly by relying on electric assistance when needed.
  • Improved Fitness: Use the pedal assist to customize your workout intensity and reach new fitness goals.
  • Eco-Friendly Transportation: Reduce your carbon footprint by choosing a more sustainable mode of transportation.

Usage

Installing this conversion kit involves replacing your existing bottom bracket with the included motor unit. The kit comes with comprehensive instructions and wiring diagrams to guide you through the process. The motor is controlled by a separate display unit (sold separately), allowing you to adjust assist levels, monitor battery life, and access other features.

Once installed, you can enjoy a new level of riding experience, effortlessly tackling challenging terrain and exploring further distances.

titre: Bafang CAN 48V 500W Motor Brushless Mid Drive eBike Engine BBS02B BBS02 Electric Bicycle Conversion Kits 20Ah Lithium Battery
titre_nb_auto: Bafang CAN 48V 500W motor børsteløs midtdrev elsykkelmotor BBS02B BBS02 elektrisk sykkelkonverteringssett 20Ah litiumbatteri
description:
Features

The Bafang CAN 48V 500W Motor Brushless Mid Drive eBike Engine BBS02B is a powerful and versatile conversion kit designed to transform your bicycle into an electric bike. This mid-drive motor offers a smooth and natural riding experience, seamlessly blending with your pedaling power.

  • Brushless Motor: This type of motor delivers efficient power transfer and quiet operation, ensuring a comfortable ride.
  • CAN Interface: This interface allows for advanced communication between the motor, display, and battery, enabling precise control and performance monitoring.
  • Mid-Drive Placement: The motor is located in the middle of the bike, near the crankset. This placement provides optimal weight distribution and efficient power transfer to the pedals, mimicking a natural riding sensation.

Specifications

The Bafang CAN 48V 500W Motor Brushless Mid Drive eBike Engine BBS02B is built with robust specifications for reliable performance:

  • Voltage: 48V
  • Power Output: 500W
  • Display Compatibility: The motor supports compatible displays to provide riders with real-time information about speed, distance, battery level, and other essential data.
  • Battery Capacity: This kit includes a powerful 20Ah Lithium Battery, providing ample range for extended rides.

Benefits

Experience the numerous advantages of upgrading your bicycle with this conversion kit:

  • Effortless Pedaling: The 500W motor significantly reduces pedaling effort, making hills and long distances a breeze.
  • Increased Range: The high-capacity lithium battery provides extended range for your rides, allowing you to explore further without worrying about running out of power.
  • Improved Performance: Enjoy enhanced speed and acceleration capabilities, transforming your daily commute or leisure ride into an exciting experience.
  • Eco-Friendly Transportation: Reduce your carbon footprint by choosing a more sustainable mode of transportation.

Usage

This conversion kit is designed for easy installation on compatible bicycles. The comprehensive instruction manual guides you through the process, ensuring a smooth and successful conversion.

Once installed, simply select your desired assist level using the provided display controls and enjoy the convenience of electric-powered cycling. Remember to always follow local regulations and safety guidelines when operating an eBike.

  • Børsteløs motor: Denne typen motor gir effektiv kraftoverføring og stillegående drift, noe som sikrer en komfortabel tur.
  • CAN-grensesnitt: Dette grensesnittet muliggjør avansert kommunikasjon mellom motor, display og batteri, noe som muliggjør presis kontroll og ytelsesovervåking.

Fordeler

Opplev de mange fordelene ved å oppgradere sykkelen din med dette konverteringssettet:

  • Forbedret ytelse: Nyt forbedrede hastighets- og akselerasjonsegenskaper, og forvandle din daglige pendling eller fritidstur til en spennende opplevelse.

titre: Varstrom 48V1000W Rear Hub Motor Kit Gear Brushelss 26 27.5 28 29inch Electric Bicycle Conversion Kit eBike 13Ah 20Ah Battery
titre_nb_auto: Varstrom 48V1000W baknavmotorsett gir børsteløs 26 27,5 28 29 tommers elsykkelkonverteringssett elsykkel 13Ah 20Ah batteri
description:
Features

The Varstrom 48V 1000W Rear Hub Motor Kit is your gateway to electrifying your bicycle! This comprehensive kit empowers you to convert your existing 26, 27.5, 28, or 29-inch bike into a powerful electric eBike.

  • Powerful Brushless Hub Motor: Experience exhilarating acceleration and effortless climbing with the high-torque brushless motor, providing 1000 watts of power.
  • Reliable Gear System: The integrated gear system ensures smooth and efficient power delivery across a wide range of riding conditions.
  • Multiple Battery Options: Choose from two battery capacities 13Ah or 20Ah to tailor the range and performance to your needs.

Specifications

This kit is designed for optimal compatibility and performance:

  • Voltage: 48V
  • Motor Power: 1000W
  • Wheel Size Compatibility: 26, 27.5, 28, and 29 inches
  • Battery Options: 13Ah and 20Ah

Benefits

Converting your bike to an eBike unlocks a world of advantages:

  • Effortless Commuting: Tackle hills with ease and arrive at your destination feeling refreshed, even on longer journeys.
  • Increased Range: Extend your cycling adventures with the power of the electric motor.
  • Enhanced Exploration: Discover new routes and ride further than ever before.

Usage

The Varstrom 48V 1000W Rear Hub Motor Kit is designed for straightforward installation.

With the included instructions and components, you can transform your bike into a powerful eBike with relative ease.
description_nb_auto:
Funksjoner

Varstrom 48V 1000W baknavmotorsett er din inngangsport til å elektrifisere sykkelen din! Dette omfattende settet lar deg konvertere din eksisterende 26, 27,5, 28 eller 29-tommers sykkel til en kraftig elektrisk elsykkel.

  • Kraftig børsteløs navmotor: Opplev spennende akselerasjon og uanstrengt klatring med den børsteløse motoren med høyt dreiemoment, som gir 1000 watt kraft.
  • Pålitelig girsystem: Det integrerte girsystemet sikrer jevn og effektiv kraftlevering over et bredt spekter av kjøreforhold.
  • Flere batterialternativer: Velg mellom to batterikapasiteter på 13 Ah eller 20 Ah for å skreddersy rekkevidden og ytelsen til dine behov.

Spesifikasjoner

Dette settet er designet for optimal kompatibilitet og ytelse:

  • Spenning: 48V
  • Motoreffekt: 1000W
  • Hjulstørrelseskompatibilitet: 26, 27,5, 28 og 29 tommer
  • Batterialternativer: 13Ah og 20Ah

Fordeler

Å konvertere sykkelen din til en elsykkel gir deg en verden av fordeler:

  • Enkel pendling: Takle bakker med letthet og kom frem til reisemålet ditt uthvilt, selv på lengre turer.
  • Økt rekkevidde: Forleng sykkeleventyrene dine med kraften fra den elektriske motoren.
  • Forbedret utforskning: Oppdag nye ruter og sykle lenger enn noen gang før.

Bruk

Varstrom 48V 1000W baknavmotorsett er designet for enkel installasjon.

Med de inkluderte instruksjonene og komponentene kan du relativt enkelt forvandle sykkelen din til en kraftig elsykkel.

titre: Ebike Display For Bafang 8FUN BBS01 BBS01B BBS02 BBS02B BBSHD 1000W 750W 500W 250W Mid Motor Ebike Parts with CAN Protocol
titre_nb_auto: Elsykkelskjerm for Bafang 8FUN BBS01 BBS01B BBS02 BBS02B BBSHD 1000W 750W 500W 250W midtmotor elsykkeldeler med CAN-protokoll
description:
Features

This ebike display is specifically designed to work seamlessly with Bafang 8FUN mid-drive motors, including the popular BBS01, BBS01B, BBS02, BBS02B, and BBSHD models. It features a user-friendly interface that provides all the essential information you need to control your ebike effectively.

  • CAN Protocol Support: Ensures smooth and reliable communication between the display and your Bafang motor for optimal performance.
  • Multiple Display Modes: Easily switch between various display modes to view information like speed, distance, battery level, assistance level, and more.
  • Intuitive Controls: Convenient buttons allow you to navigate through menus, adjust settings, and control your ebike's features with ease.

Specifications

This display is built to withstand the demands of ebike riding.

  • Compatible with a wide range of Bafang 8FUN motors (BBS01, BBS01B, BBS02, BBS02B, BBSHD) with varying power outputs (1000W, 750W, 500W, and 250W).
  • Durable construction designed to resist wear and tear.
  • Bright display for clear visibility in various lighting conditions.

Benefits

This ebike display enhances your riding experience by providing essential information and intuitive controls.

  • Real-Time Data: Stay informed about your speed, distance traveled, battery level, and assistance level for a more enjoyable and efficient ride.
  • Enhanced Control: Easily adjust settings and features to customize your riding experience to your preferences.
  • Improved Safety: Monitor your battery status and assist levels to ensure you have enough power throughout your ride.

Usage

Installation is straightforward, connecting directly to your Bafang 8FUN mid-drive motor. The user-friendly interface allows for easy navigation and adjustment of settings. Refer to the provided instructions for detailed installation and operation guidelines.
description_nb_auto:
Funksjoner

Denne elsykkelskjermen er spesielt designet for å fungere sømløst med Bafang 8FUN midtmotorer, inkludert de populære modellene BBS01, BBS01B, BBS02, BBS02B og BBSHD. Den har et brukervennlig grensesnitt som gir all viktig informasjon du trenger for å kontrollere elsykkelen din effektivt.

  • CAN-protokollstøtte: Sikrer jevn og pålitelig kommunikasjon mellom skjermen og Bafang-motoren for optimal ytelse.
  • Flere skjermmoduser: Bytt enkelt mellom forskjellige skjermmoduser for å vise informasjon som hastighet, distanse, batterinivå, assistansenivå og mer.
  • Intuitive kontroller: Praktiske knapper lar deg navigere gjennom menyer, justere innstillinger og kontrollere elsykkelens funksjoner med letthet.

Spesifikasjoner

Denne skjermen er bygget for å tåle kravene til elsykkelkjøring.

  • Kompatibel med et bredt utvalg av Bafang 8FUN-motorer (BBS01, BBS01B, BBS02, BBS02B, BBSHD) med varierende effekt (1000 W, 750 W, 500 W og 250 W).
  • Slitesterk konstruksjon designet for å motstå slitasje.
  • Lysst display for tydelig synlighet under forskjellige lysforhold.

Fordeler

Denne elsykkeldisplayen forbedrer kjøreopplevelsen din ved å gi viktig informasjon og intuitive kontroller.

  • Sanntidsdata: Hold deg informert om hastighet, tilbakelagt distanse, batterinivå og assistansenivå for en mer behagelig og effektiv tur.
  • Forbedret kontroll: Juster enkelt innstillinger og funksjoner for å tilpasse kjøreopplevelsen din til dine preferanser.
  • Forbedret sikkerhet: Overvåk batteristatus og assistansenivåer for å sikre at du har nok strøm gjennom hele turen.

Bruk

Installasjonen er enkel, og kobles direkte til Bafang 8FUN midtmotoren. Det brukervennlige grensesnittet gir enkel navigering og justering av innstillinger. Se de medfølgende instruksjonene for detaljerte retningslinjer for installasjon og bruk.

titre: Varstrom 125XV 48V 750W 500W Rear Hub Motor Kit 20 26 27.5 700C Electric Bicycle 16Ah 20Ah Cassette V Brake Bike Conversion Kit
titre_nb_auto: Varstrom 125XV 48V 750W 500W baknavmotorsett 20 26 27,5 700C elsykkel 16Ah 20Ah kassett V-brems sykkelkonverteringssett
description:
Features

The Varstrom 125XV E-Bike Conversion Kit is designed to seamlessly transform your traditional bicycle into a powerful electric ride. This comprehensive kit equips your bike with everything you need for an exhilarating e-bike experience.

  • Rear Hub Motor: A high-performance 750W rear hub motor provides ample power for effortless hill climbing and cruising at various speeds.
  • Battery Options: Choose from two convenient battery capacities: a 16Ah or a 20Ah lithium-ion battery pack, offering extended range for your rides.
  • Cassette Selection: A wide range cassette provides optimal gear ratios for diverse terrains and riding styles, ensuring smooth transitions between gears.
  • V-Brake System: Reliable V-brakes ensure safe and controlled stopping power in a variety of conditions.

Specifications

This kit is compatible with various wheel sizes and comes equipped with a 48V system for optimal performance.

  • Motor Power: 750W Peak, 500W Continuous
  • Voltage: 48V
  • Wheel Size Compatibility: 20", 26", 27.5", 700C
  • Battery Capacity Options: 16Ah or 20Ah

Benefits

By converting your existing bicycle, you gain a multitude of advantages:

  • Extended Range: Enjoy longer rides without the fatigue of pedaling solely.
  • Effortless Hill Climbing: Conquering steep inclines becomes a breeze with the powerful electric assist.
  • Increased Commuting Efficiency: Arrive at your destination refreshed and on time, even with challenging routes.

Usage

Installing the Varstrom 125XV E-Bike Conversion Kit is a relatively straightforward process that can be accomplished by following the provided instructions. This kit empowers you to personalize your cycling experience by adding electric assistance to any compatible bicycle, allowing for greater versatility and enjoyment on every ride.
description_nb_auto:
Funksjoner

Varstrom 125XV elsykkelkonverteringssett er utviklet for å sømløst forvandle din tradisjonelle sykkel til en kraftig elektrisk sykkel. Dette omfattende settet utstyrer sykkelen din med alt du trenger for en spennende elsykkelopplevelse.

  • Navmotor bak: En høytytende 750 W navmotor bak gir rikelig med kraft for uanstrengt bakkekjøring og cruising i forskjellige hastigheter.
  • Batterialternativer: Velg mellom to praktiske batterikapasiteter: en 16 Ah eller en 20 Ah litiumionbatteripakke, som gir utvidet rekkevidde for turene dine.
  • Kassettvalg: En kassett med bredt girutvekslingsområde gir optimale girforhold for ulike terreng og kjørestiler, noe som sikrer jevne overganger mellom gir.
  • V-bremsesystem: Pålitelige V-bremser sikrer sikker og kontrollert bremsekraft under en rekke forhold.

Spesifikasjoner

Dette settet er kompatibelt med forskjellige hjulstørrelser og er utstyrt med et 48 V-system for optimal ytelse.

  • Motoreffekt: 750 W topp, 500 W kontinuerlig
  • Spenning: 48V
  • Kompatibilitet med hjulstørrelser: 20", 26", 27,5", 700C
  • Alternativer for batterikapasitet: 16Ah eller 20Ah

Fordeler

Ved å konvertere din eksisterende sykkel får du en rekke fordeler:

  • Utvidet rekkevidde: Nyt lengre turer uten å bli sliten av å bare tråkke.
  • Uanstrengt bakkeklatring: Å mestre bratte bakker blir en lek med den kraftige elektriske assistansen.
  • Økt pendlingseffektivitet: Kom frem til destinasjonen din uthvilt og i tide, selv på utfordrende ruter.

Bruk

Installering av Varstrom 125XV elsykkelkonverteringssett er en relativt enkel prosess som kan oppnås ved å følge de medfølgende instruksjonene. Dette settet lar deg tilpasse sykkelopplevelsen din ved å legge til elektrisk assistanse til enhver kompatibel sykkel, noe som gir større allsidighet og glede på alle ri.

description_short:
Unleash the power of electric cycling with the Varstrom TSDZ Series Mid Motor Kits. Engineered for seamless integration and exhilarating performance, these kits transform your bicycle into a sleek, efficient e-bike.

description:
Features

The Bafang 750W 48V Motor Kit is a comprehensive solution for converting your bicycle into an electric bike. Designed with power and performance in mind, this kit features the robust Bafang BBS02 or BBS02B motor, known for its durability and exceptional torque output. The central drive location ensures optimal weight distribution and a natural riding experience.

  • 750W High-Power Motor: Experience exhilarating acceleration and effortless uphill climbs with the powerful 750W motor.
  • 48V System Voltage: Optimized for efficiency and performance, delivering ample power throughout your rides.
  • BBS02 or BBS02B Motor Option: Choose between the highly reliable and efficient BBS02 or the advanced BBS02B motor with integrated display functionality.
  • Central Drive Placement: Provides balanced weight distribution for a natural and responsive riding experience.

Specifications

This Bafang motor kit utilizes proven components to deliver a reliable and efficient electric biking experience.

  • Motor Type: Brushless geared hub
  • Voltage: 48V
  • Power Output: 750W
  • Maximum Torque: High torque output for effortless climbing and acceleration
  • Chainring Compatibility: Wide range of chainring options available to customize your gearing

Benefits

Transform your bicycle into a powerful electric bike and enjoy numerous benefits:

  • Effortless Commuting: Conquer hills and long distances with ease, making your daily commute more enjoyable.
  • Increased Range: The 48V system and efficient motor provide extended range for longer adventures.
  • Enhanced Performance: Experience exhilarating acceleration and top speeds to make every ride exciting.
  • Reduced Physical Strain: Pedal less and enjoy a comfortable ride, ideal for riders of all fitness levels.

Usage

Installing this Bafang motor kit requires some mechanical knowledge and tools. It involves replacing your existing crankset with the provided Bafang motor assembly. Detailed instructions are included to guide you through the installation process. Proper wiring and connection to a compatible battery pack are essential for safe and successful operation.

Once installed, the system can be controlled via a separate display (for BBS02B) or by using a thumb throttle. The Bafang 750W motor kit offers several assistance modes, allowing you to customize your pedaling effort based on your needs and preferences.

  • Voltage Flexibility: Compatible with both 36V and 48V battery systems, allowing you to select the voltage that best suits your preferences and riding conditions.
  • Battery Capacity Options: This kit is available with either a 13Ah or 20Ah battery pack, providing extended range for longer rides.

Specifications

The Tongsheng TSDZ8 TSDZ2B Ebike Kit boasts a robust set of specifications designed for performance and reliability:

  • Motor Power: 250W, 500W, or 750W
  • Voltage Compatibility: 36V or 48V
  • Battery Capacity Options: 13Ah or 20Ah
  • Drive System Type: Central Mid-Motor
  • Sensor Type: Torque Sensor

Benefits

The Tongsheng TSDZ8 TSDZ2B Ebike Kit offers numerous benefits for cyclists of all levels:

  • Enhanced Riding Experience: Enjoy effortless pedaling, conquer hills with ease, and reduce fatigue on longer rides.
  • Increased Range and Versatility: Choose the battery capacity that best suits your needs and explore further distances.
  • Improved Efficiency: Maximize your pedal power and save energy by utilizing the motor's assistance.
  • Eco-Friendly Transportation: Reduce reliance on fossil fuels and make a positive impact on the environment.

Usage

The Tongsheng TSDZ8 TSDZ2B Ebike Kit is designed for easy installation onto most standard bicycles. The torque sensor seamlessly integrates with your pedaling motion, providing natural and responsive power assistance. Adjust the assist level using the included controller to customize your riding experience.

For optimal performance, follow the manufacturer's instructions carefully during installation and maintenance.

Transform your cycling experience with the numerous benefits this electric conversion kit offers:

  • Effortless Riding: Easily conquer hills and maintain speed with the powerful motor assistance, reducing fatigue on long rides.

  • Versatile Performance: Tackle various terrains with confidence, from paved roads to challenging off-road trails.

Usage

Installing this conversion kit is a straightforward process that typically involves attaching the motor to your bike's existing bottom bracket and connecting it to a compatible battery system. The included display unit provides information on speed, battery level, and assist mode.

description:
Features

The Varstrom Tongsheng TSDZ16, TSDZ8, and TSDZ2B Mid Motor Kits offer a powerful and efficient way to upgrade your bicycle to an ebike. These kits feature a central torque sensor that intelligently adjusts motor assistance based on your pedaling effort, providing a natural and responsive riding experience.

  • Central Torque Sensor: Detects your pedaling force for smooth and natural power delivery.
  • Multiple Motor Power Options: Available in 500W, 750W, and 1000W to suit your riding needs and terrain.
  • Integrated Battery Options: Includes both 13Ah and 20Ah battery capacities for extended riding range.
  • Designed for Versatility: Compatible with a wide range of bicycles, allowing you to easily convert your existing bike into an ebike.

Specifications

The Varstrom Tongsheng TSDZ series boasts several key specifications:

  • Motor Types: TSDZ16, TSDZ8, and TSDZ2B
  • Voltage: 48V
  • Power Output: 500W, 750W, or 1000W (depending on model)
  • Battery Capacity: 13Ah or 20Ah (depending on model)
  • Sensor Type: Central Torque Sensor

Benefits

These mid-drive motor kits offer numerous benefits for cyclists:

  • Increased Pedaling Efficiency: The powerful motor assists your pedaling, making hills and long distances easier to conquer.
  • Enhanced Riding Experience: The torque sensor provides smooth and natural power delivery, mimicking the feeling of traditional cycling.
  • Extended Range: Choose from 13Ah or 20Ah battery options for longer rides without needing to recharge frequently.
  • Eco-Friendly Transportation: Reduce your carbon footprint by opting for an electric bike powered by a rechargeable battery.

Usage

The Varstrom Tongsheng TSDZ16, TSDZ8, and TSDZ2B kits are designed to be easily installed on various bicycles. Following the provided instructions, you can seamlessly integrate the motor, battery, and controller into your bike's frame. Once installed, simply pedal as usual, and the motor will provide assistance based on your pedaling force.

These kits are ideal for commuters, recreational riders, and anyone seeking a more efficient and enjoyable cycling experience.
description_nb_auto:

Varstrom Tongsheng TSDZ16, TSDZ8 og TSDZ2B midtmotorsett tilbyr en kraftig og effektiv måte å oppgradere sykkelen din til en elsykkel. Disse settene har en sentral momentsensor som intelligent justerer motorassistansen basert på pedalinnsatsen din, noe som gir en naturlig og responsiv kjøreopplevelse.

  • Sentral momentsensor: Registrerer pedalkraften din for jevn og naturlig kraftlevering.

  • Motortyper: TSDZ16, TSDZ8 og TSDZ2B
  • Spenning: 48V
  • Effekt: 500W, 750W eller 1000W (avhengig av modell)
  • Batterikapasitet: 13Ah eller 20Ah (avhengig av modell)
  • Sensortype: Sentral momentsensor

Fordeler

Disse midtmotorsettene tilbyr en rekke fordeler for syklister:

  • Økt tråkkeeffektivitet: Den kraftige motoren hjelper deg med tråkkingen, noe som gjør bakker og lange distanser lettere å mestre.

  • Utvidet rekkevidde: Velg mellom 13Ah- eller 20Ah-batterialternativer for lengre turer uten å måtte lade ofte.
  • Miljøvennlig transport: Reduser karbonavtrykket ditt ved å velge en elsykkel drevet av et oppladbart batteri.

Bruk

Varstrom Tongsheng TSDZ16-, TSDZ8- og TSDZ2B-settene er designet for å enkelt kunne monteres på ulike sykler. Ved å følge de medfølgende instruksjonene kan du sømløst integrere motoren, batteriet og kontrolleren i sykkelens ramme. Disse settene er ideelle for pendlere, fritidssyklister og alle som ønsker en mer effektiv og hyggelig sykkelopplevelse.

Slipp løs kraften i ditt neste eventyr med Bafang Rear Hub Motor 48V 1000W G062.1000 DC elektrisk sykkelkonverteringssett. Dette settet er designet for å forvandle enhver kompatibel fatbike (20"/26") til en høytytende elektrisk sykkel, klar for å takle utfordrende terreng og utforske nye horisonter.

Med en robust 1000W motor og et kraftig 48V-system, gir dette konverteringssettet en spennende opplevelse med uanstrengt akselerasjon og imponerende klatrekraft. Den inkluderte skivebremsen forbedrer sikkerhet og kontroll, slik at du trygt kan navigere i alle stier og veiforhold.

  • Kraftig 1000 W motor: Bekjemp bakker og hindringer med letthet, og nyt uanstrengte klatringer og dynamisk ytelse.
  • 48V system: Opplev utvidet rekkevidde og overlegen kraftlevering for en virkelig altoppslukende elektrisk sykkel.
  • Skivebremsesystem: Nyt forbedret sikkerhet og presis kontroll for trygg håndtering under ulike forhold.
  • Designet for 20"/26" fatbikes: Integrer dette konverteringssettet sømløst i din eksisterende fatbike-ramme for en umiddelbar kraftøkning.

Oppgrader fatbiken din i dag med Bafang baknavmotorkonverteringssett og lås opp en verden av spennende offroad-eventyr.
